prompts.frontCover: An over-the-top, funny anime romantic comedy scene illustrated in a vibrant watercolor style. A man and a woman are depicted as charming cartoon anime characters. The man, wearing glasses and a light-colored t-shirt, stands with a comically exaggerated lovestruck expression, his eyes wide with sparkling heart shapes in them. He is presenting a small, perfectly wrapped birthday gift with a big bow. The woman, wearing a dark top, reacts with a playful, slightly flustered "tsundere" expression—one eyebrow raised, a slight blush on her cheeks, trying to look unimpressed but secretly delighted. The entire scene is drenched in shōjo anime aesthetics: a flurry of delicate pink cherry blossom petals swirls around them, and the air is filled with dramatic sparkle effects, glitter, and speed lines to emphasize the comedic romance. The background is a soft wash of watercolor pastels, suggesting a park setting. In the center, the text "Happy Birthday, My Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script, colored in a deep magenta. The overall composition is dynamic, humorous, and full of romantic energy, rendered with the soft edges and flowing colors of a 2D watercolor painting.
